    <summaries>
      <billSummaries>
        <item>
          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Business Relief from Disease Induced Economic Hardship Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Act to expand the definition of a &quot;disaster&quot; for which the Small Business Administration may provide disaster loans to small business concerns to include communicable diseases for which the federal government issues a travel alert or travel warning.</p>  <p>]]></text>
          <actionDate>2017-01-17</actionDate>
          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2017-07-11T21:31:27Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
          <updateDate>2017-01-17T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in Senate</name>
        </item>
        <item>
          <versionCode>80</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>(This measure has not been amended since it was introduced. The summary has been expanded because action occurred on the measure.)</p> <p><b>Small Business Relief from Disease Induced Economic Hardship Act of 2017</b></p> <p>(Sec. 2) This bill amends the Small Business Act to expand the definition of a &quot;disaster&quot; for which the Small Business Administration may provide disaster loans to small business concerns to include communicable diseases for which the federal government issues a travel alert or travel warning.</p>]]></text>
